a couple of days.

501
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:04,200
Jadi tidak lama lagi?

502
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:12,680
Then you will be able
to see Chi Cheng soon.

503
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,560
Mengapa anda kelihatan tidak berpuas hati?

504
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,680
I do not know.

505
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,640
Saya hanya sedikit bingung.

506
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:23,280
Maybe it is been too
long since I last saw him.

507
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:33,800
Siapa di sini?

508
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:36,880
Anda akan tahu bila anda melihatnya.

509
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,640
Have a seat.

510
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:23,240
Mengapa anda menurunkan berat badan?

511
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:39,720
Did you miss me?

512
00:32:40,840 --> 00:32:42,040
Apa pendapat anda?

513
00:32:43,520 --> 00:32:44,520
How would I know?

514
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:50,280
Saya rindu awak.

515
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:54,880
Did you miss me?

516
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:55,960
Saya buat.

517
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:58,600
How much?

518
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,280
Saya sangat merindui awak...

519
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:05,480
that I handed over
my little treasury.

520
00:33:10,120 --> 00:33:11,120
Apa yang anda katakan?

521
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:13,520
It is nothing.

522
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:16,280
Kes anda akan dibicarakan
dalam masa dua hari.

523
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:21,360
Besides the little treasury,

524
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:22,720
Apa lagi yang anda berputus asa?

525
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,440
The old house.

526
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,520
Mengapa anda tidak menjual rumah saya?

527
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:45,200
I do not want your family
to look down on me.

528
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:46,880
Kemudian meminjam wang dari Cheng Yu.

529
00:33:48,080 --> 00:33:50,000
It is because the
two of us are family.

530
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:58,720
Anda selalu berkata...

531
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,320
I am a cheapskate...

532
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,560
Siapa yang tidak menghabiskan apa -apa.

533
00:34:02,120 --> 00:34:04,320
This time, I spent everything.

534
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,360
Mari lihat bagaimana anda boleh
membuang saya pada masa akan datang.

535
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,600
You are my financier.

536
00:34:12,720 --> 00:34:14,960
Selagi anda kembali,
saya boleh menjana wang.

537
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:17,960
If you stay in here, I will
suffer the biggest loss.

538
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:19,600
Jadi selepas mengira,

539
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,320
it is better to get you out of here.

540
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,680
Sebenarnya, saya juga menyesal.

541
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:44,720
I should have given you
more allowance back then.

542
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:48,400
Sekarang saya telah memberikan
wang kepada orang lain, saya sedar...

543
00:34:49,600 --> 00:34:51,600
that 10 or 20 yuan
is really nothing.

544
00:34:53,120 --> 00:34:54,120
Sebenarnya,

545
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:59,240
my little treasury
is for our retirement.

546
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:01,360
Sekiranya anda tidak dapat keluar,

547
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:04,520
Apakah penggunaan wang itu kepada saya?

548
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:06,760
So...

549
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:08,680
Saya tidak membeli kebebasan anda.

550
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,120
I am buying my own security.

551
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:12,960
Anda tahu apa?

552
00:35:12,961 --> 00:35:15,600
When I sleep at home all
alone now, I feel really scared.

553
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:19,000
Saya hanya mahu awak kembali.

554
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:21,439
I do not want a life of luxury.

555
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,640
Saya hanya mahukan awak.

556
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,360
Chi Cheng.

557
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:31,040
Katakan sesuatu.

558
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,440
Chi Cheng!

559
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,120
Katakan sesuatu.

560
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,160
I hate you.

561
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:10,400
Lihatlah anda.
You still have over 10 minutes.

562
00:36:45,080 --> 00:36:47,480
Hei, dia kembali ke sel.

563
00:36:47,560 --> 00:36:48,560
You should go too.

564
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:13,519
(Sel penjara)

565
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:14,680
1706.

566
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:15,800
Sudah tiba masanya untuk makan.

